<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.2.11">
<l>meliyunōy tīrkkunaṅ kaṇṇaṉ kaḻalkaṇmēṉ</l>
<l>malipukaḻ vaṇkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉcol</l>
<l>lolipuka ḻāyirat tippattum vallavar</l>
<l>malipukaḻ vāṉavark kāvarnaṟ kōvaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these ten from the thousand of resounding praise</l>
<l>spoken by Caṭakōpaṉ from liberal Kurukūr as ample praise</l>
<l>on the anklets of our Kaṇṇaṉ that will end weakening pain,</l>
<l>will be [part of] the good string of celestials with ample praise.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
